year ended December 31, 2019 reflects the results of both Praxair and Linde AG for the entire year. The year ended December 31,
2018 reflects the results of Praxair for the entire year and the results of Linde AG for the period beginning after October 31, 2018
(the merger date), including the impacts of purchase accounting (See Notes 1, 3 and 4 to the consolidated financial statements). The
historical periods prior to 2018 reflect the results of Praxair. Prior periods presented have been recast to be consistent with the new
segment structure:
